name: Cactus Dino Run
description:
Play as an unstoppable dinosaur running through a desert full of deadly cacti!

Use A/D or Left/Right Arrows to move horizontally while trying to avoid hitting the cacti as you move increansingly faster.

*Warning* I'm not sure if I will keep the browser version because, when I tested it, it was very slow. If it is still here, I recommend playing the downloadable version for a better experience.

*This game was made in a few days for Low Effort Jam 6*
